{"type":null,"faqId":47133,"title":"手机无法获取到荣耀小K手表位置信息，是什么原因？","answer":"<p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';text-align:left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\ncolor:black\">APP</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">上提示“未能连接手表”或手表定位不刷新，极有可能是手表欠费或者关机了，请按以下步骤排查：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';text-align:left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\ncolor:black\"><img width=\"267\" height=\"462\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20151016150925707001.jpg\" alt=\"http://w3.huawei.com/tkbmng/ha-i/7394b_ocdcn.jpg\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';text-align:left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\ncolor:black\">1.</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">若手表是关机状态，请按手表侧键<span>3s</span>开启手表之后，点击<span>APP</span>右上角的手动定位刷新</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';text-align:left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\ncolor:black\">2.</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">若手表开机，查看手表时间是否是当前时间，若不是，说明手表数据网络不通。看下手表<span>SIM</span>卡是不是欠费了，若欠费，请续交话费后长按手表侧键<span>10s</span>重启手表</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';text-align:left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\ncolor:black\">3. </span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">如果手表时间显示的是当前时间，但定位仍然刷新失败，看下是不是手机数据业务异常，这也可能导致位置信息无法及时从云服务器获取</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif';text-align:left\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;\ncolor:black\">4.</span><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black\">请长按手表侧键<span>10s</span>重启手表，可以取出<span>SIM</span>卡重新安装一次，再长按手表侧键<span>10s</span>重启手表</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Calibri','sans-serif'\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt;font-family:宋体;color:black;\nbackground:white\">若定位始终不能刷新，请用户反馈手表<span>IMEI</span>号、<span>APP</span>版本号，上升研发处理。</span></p>\n<br>\n</p>","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2653","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444979293000,"seriesProductName":"K1-G01","visitedTimes":24,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"K1-G01,荣耀小K,儿童手表,K1,位置,手表位置,刷新,无法获取","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}